---
import PageLayout from "@/layouts/Base.astro";

const meta = {
    description: "Java/Python开发者 | 十年技术沉淀 | 代码与生活随笔",
    title: "关于",
};
---

<PageLayout meta={meta}>

    <h1 class="title mb-6">关于</h1>
    <div class="prose prose-citrus max-w-none">
        <p class="font-medium">
            专注于Java/Python的全栈工程师，十年企业级应用开发经验，专注高并发与分布式系统设计。
        </p>
        
        <div class="my-6 space-y-4">
            <div class="flex items-start">
                <div>
                    <h4 class="font-semibold">技术栈</h4>
                    <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mt-2">
                        <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-gray-100 rounded-full text-sm">SpringBoot</span>
                        <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-gray-100 rounded-full text-sm">MyBatis</span>
                        <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-gray-100 rounded-full text-sm">FastAPI</span>
                        <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-gray-100 rounded-full text-sm">Astro</span>
                        <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-gray-100 rounded-full text-sm">Vue</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="flex items-start">
                <div>
                    <h4 class="font-semibold">近期探索</h4>
                    <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mt-2">
                        <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-blue-50 rounded-full text-sm">云原生架构</span>
                        <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-blue-50 rounded-full text-sm">智能体开发</span>
                        <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-blue-50 rounded-full text-sm">技术写作</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="flex items-start">
                <div>
                    <h4 class="font-semibold">生活志趣</h4>
                    <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mt-2">
                        <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-amber-50 rounded-full text-sm">AI生成艺术</span>
                        <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-amber-50 rounded-full text-sm">科技哲学</span>
                        <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-amber-50 rounded-full text-sm">DNF</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <p class="border-t pt-4 italic">
            相信"代码是理性的诗行"，在这里记录技术洞见、项目复盘，也分享生活与键盘之外的思考痕迹。
        </p>
    </div>

</PageLayout>